{"tid":664003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"父母偏心，可以點釋懷","createTime":"2018-05-13T17:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T05:05:20.000Z","uid":39915,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"417417bc589d6b92c9b0bc6a7267720306955fa3","tid":664003,"uid":39915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"老豆咩都唔理，主要係老母偏心<br />\n明明我為屋企付出更多更上心，屋企有咩問題就我出聲，我搞，家務我都有份幫手，而細佬只顧住吃喝玩樂，老母永遠就哂佢，咩都為佢著想先<br />\n<br />\n我對細佬無怨言，只係對老母偏心嘅行為覺得唔甘心。雖然平時老母都錫我，但佢偏心嘅小動作真係令人好難受，尤其係佢以為我睇唔出，側側膊咁做出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要扮到坦然接受真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人都有相同經歷分享下？<br />\n點先可以令自己個心舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，兩兄弟都已成年"},{"pid":"df93e1cb46a20449492eae2a4bd55a627dd34fa9","tid":664003,"uid":124256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你角色一樣<br />\n都係有個仆街細佬<br />\n已經同屋企反哂面<br />\n成間冇人會講嘢咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5426eb62535fcc3bdcc7b34eb20537bfd4547b","tid":664003,"uid":39915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df93e1cb46a20449492eae2a4bd55a627dd34fa9","tid":664003,"uid":124256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你角色一樣<br />\n都係有個仆街細佬<br />\n已經同屋企反哂面<br />\n成間冇人會講嘢咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"去到反面，應該偏心得嚴重過我好多<br />\n我暫時係個心唔舒服，想叫佢公平d但又覺得自己無資格要求人地點對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9858e9300060e4a696728e4616a89a685bf0782","tid":664003,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:23:31.000Z","msg":"